<div class="add-padding-vertical-5 add-border-bottom">
    <div class="help-breadcrumb">
        <a href="~/Help/Cloud">Cloud</a> <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right glyphicon-small"></span> Cloud Dashboard
    </div>
</div>

<div class="add-padding-top help-text">
    <h2 class="add-padding-bottom-5">
        Dashboard
    </h2>
    <p>
        The Dashboard contains summary data for all of your active projects, quick links to your favorite reports, and notifications of items that require your attention.
    </p>
    <p>
        Click <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign text-color-1"></span> below for more details.
    </p>
</div>

